⍝ dyadic operator ----------------------------------

∇z←(f glue l) r
 ⍝ From Intro to APL2, p72
 z←l f r
∇

∇z←(f AND g) r
 ⍝From Intro to APL p72
 z←(f r)(g r)
∇

      (*glue 2) AND+ 0 1 2
 1 2 4  0 1 2 

      *glue 2 AND+ 0 1 2
 1 2 4  0 1 2 

      )ERASE glue AND

⍝ bracked index and function axis

∇Z←A DyMon B
⊃('Monadic' 'Dyadic')[Z←,1+0≠⎕NC 'A']
∇

      +/ DyMon 1
Monadic
1

      +/[1] DyMon 1
Monadic
1

      (+/[1]) DyMon 1
Monadic
1

      (1 2 3)[1] DyMon 1
Dyadic
2

