⍝ IBM APL2 compatibility ----------------------------------

      ∇Z←SHOW_NC B¯B;N
       N←8↑B,':'
       →(¯1 0 1 2 3 4 = ⎕NC B¯B)/I U L V F O ◊ ++
      I: →0, Z←(8↑B), ': Invalid Name'
      U: →0, Z←(8↑B), ': Unused Name'
      L: →0, Z←(8↑B), ': Label'
      V: →0, Z←(8↑B), ': Value', ⍎B¯B
      F: →0, Z←(8↑B), ': Function'
      O: →0, Z←(8↑B), ': Operator'
      ∇

      ∇Z←A (LO OPER1) B
       SHOW_NC 'A'
       SHOW_NC 'LO'
       SHOW_NC 'OPER1'
       SHOW_NC 'B'
      ∇

      ∇Z←A (LO OPER2 RO) B
       SHOW_NC 'A'
       SHOW_NC 'LO'
       SHOW_NC 'OPER1'
       SHOW_NC 'RO'
       SHOW_NC 'B'
      ∇

      ⊣««« NOTE: IBM APL2 gives:

      ⍝ binding of bracket index
      ⍝
      1 2 3[2]
RANK ERROR

      ⍝ binding of left operand (literal)
      ⍝
      11 22 33 OPER1 1 2 3
A       : Unused Name
LO      : Value  11 22 33
OPER1   : Operator
B       : Value  1 2 3

      ⍝ binding of left operand (parser)
      ⍝
      (UU VV WW)←11 22 33
A       : Unused Name
LO      : Value  11 22 33
OPER1   : Operator
B       : Value  1 2 3

      ⍝ binding of left operand (in parentheses)
      ⍝
      11 22 (33 OPER1) 1 2 3
A       : 11
LO      : Value  22 33
OPER1   : Operator
B       : Value  1 2 3

      ⍝ binding of left and right operands (literal)
      ⍝
      11 22 33 'lop' OPER2 'rop' 1 2 3
A:      Value Unused Name
LO:     Value lop
OPER1:  Operator
RO:     Value rop
B:      Value 1 2 3
       »»»


